  "detailed_description": "TV Kid is an addicting roguelike clicker game with endless possibilities for item combinations!<br>Click through channel after channel and try to defeat television itself!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1678860/extras/246b34c617115799b30975e91bd0b92d.avif?t=1763066843\" width=384 height=124 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >List of Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Every single run is completely randomized and different!<br></li><li>100+ items to find and collect!<br></li><li>3+ characters to unlock and play as!<br></li><li>25+ monsters to find and defeat!<br></li><li>Includes a waifu body pillow!</li></ul>",
